        "description": "TOTALLY BASKETBALL lets you play the full sport of Basketball in VR!  Jump for the Tip-Off! Shoot free throws! Steal the ball but don't get a Foul! This game gives you the awesome ability to control your 2 teammates when playing full court 3v3 matches. Use your buttons to move your teammates to better positions or to pass you the ball when you've got a good shot!\n\n\nFeatures:\n-Practice and tutorial modes for new players\n-Multiple teams/venues to choose from (and play against)\n-Top notch realistic shooting physics\n-Multiplayer (Play against a friend and control your own teams or play a 1 on 1 game of Horse together)\n-Customizer (Make your Avatar look as cool as you want)\n-Fun seasonal updates (Check out new stadiums and new items throughout the year)\n-Large community of people to play with or get tips from (See our Discord)\n\nCOMING SOON: 5v5 Multiplayer (up to 10 friends)\n",
